{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"XRCompositionLayer.layout","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer/layout","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebXR_Device_API\">WebXR Device API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer\"><code>XRCompositionLayer</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer/blendTextureSourceAlpha\"><code>blendTextureSourceAlpha</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer/chromaticAberrationCorrection\"><code>chromaticAberrationCorrection</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>layout</code></em></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer/mipLevels\"><code>mipLevels</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer/needsRedraw\"><code>needsRedraw</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer/destroy\"><code>destroy()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRLayer\"><code>XRLayer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for WebXR Device API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/xr\"><code>Navigator.xr</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/makeXRCompatible\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext.makeXRCompatible()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRAnchor\"><code>XRAnchor</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRBoundedReferenceSpace\"><code>XRBoundedReferenceSpace</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCPUDepthInformation\"><code>XRCPUDepthInformation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRDepthInformation\"><code>XRDepthInformation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRFrame\"><code>XRFrame</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRInputSource\"><code>XRInputSource</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRInputSourceArray\"><code>XRInputSourceArray</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRInputSourceEvent\"><code>XRInputSourceEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRInputSourcesChangeEvent\"><code>XRInputSourcesChangeEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRPose\"><code>XRPose</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRReferenceSpace\"><code>XRReferenceSpace</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRReferenceSpaceEvent\"><code>XRReferenceSpaceEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRRenderState\"><code>XRRenderState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRRigidTransform\"><code>XRRigidTransform</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSession\"><code>XRSession</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSessionEvent\"><code>XRSessionEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSpace\"><code>XRSpace</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSystem\"><code>XRSystem</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRView\"><code>XRView</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRViewerPose\"><code>XRViewerPose</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRViewport\"><code>XRViewport</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLBinding\"><code>XRWebGLBinding</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLDepthInformation\"><code>XRWebGLDepthInformation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLLayer\"><code>XRWebGLLayer</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>This is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">experimental technology</a></strong><br>Check the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility table</a> carefully before using this in production.</p></div>\n<p>The read-only <strong><code>layout</code></strong> property of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer\"><code>XRCompositionLayer</code></a> interface is the layout type of the layer.</p>\n<p>To specify the layout type of a layer, use one of the layer creation methods and their <code>layout</code> option:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLBinding/createQuadLayer\"><code>XRWebGLBinding.createQuadLayer()</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLBinding/createCylinderLayer\"><code>XRWebGLBinding.createCylinderLayer()</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLBinding/createEquirectLayer\"><code>XRWebGLBinding.createEquirectLayer()</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLBinding/createCubeLayer\"><code>XRWebGLBinding.createCubeLayer()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":false,"content":"<p>A string. Possible values:</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"default\"><code>default</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The layer accommodates all views of the session. It is recommended to use the <code>texture-array</code> texture type for <code>default</code> layouts.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"mono\"><code>mono</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A single <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSubImage\"><code>XRSubImage</code></a> is allocated and presented to both eyes.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"stereo\"><code>stereo</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The user agent decides how it allocates the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSubImage\"><code>XRSubImage</code></a> (one or two) and the layout (top/bottom or left/right). It is recommended to use the <code>texture-array</code> texture type for <code>stereo</code> layouts.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"stereo-left-right\"><code>stereo-left-right</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A single <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSubImage\"><code>XRSubImage</code></a> is allocated. Left eye gets the left area of the texture, right eye the right. This layout is designed to minimize draw calls for content that is already in stereo (for example stereo videos or images).</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"stereo-top-bottom\"><code>stereo-top-bottom</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A single <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSubImage\"><code>XRSubImage</code></a> is allocated. Left eye gets the top area of the texture, right eye the bottom. This layout is designed to minimize draw calls for content that is already in stereo (for example stereo videos or images).</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"setting_and_getting_a_layers_layout","title":"Setting and getting a layer's layout","isH3":true,"content":"<p>To specify a layer's layout, use a layer creation method (like <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLBinding/createQuadLayer\"><code>XRWebGLBinding.createQuadLayer()</code></a>) and its <code>layout</code> option. To retrieve the type of layer layout, use the <code>layout</code> property:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> layer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> xrGlBinding<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createQuadLayer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token literal-property property\">pixelWidth</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1024</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n   <span class=\"token literal-property property\">pixelHeight</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">768</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n   <span class=\"token literal-property property\">layout</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"stereo\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nlayer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>layout<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"stereo\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"query":"api.XRCompositionLayer.layout","specifications":[]}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.XRCompositionLayer.layout","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSubImage\"><code>XRSubImage</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLBinding/createQuadLayer\"><code>XRWebGLBinding.createQuadLayer()</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLBinding/createCylinderLayer\"><code>XRWebGLBinding.createCylinderLayer()</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLBinding/createEquirectLayer\"><code>XRWebGLBinding.createEquirectLayer()</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLBinding/createCubeLayer\"><code>XRWebGLBinding.createCubeLayer()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Value","id":"value"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The read-only layout property of the XRCompositionLayer interface is the layout type of the layer.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-09-09T05:23:40.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/xrcompositionlayer/layout","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/xrcompositionlayer/layout/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/073f70e052ff92ab715df3c20678c11c9b51747f","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer","title":"XRCompositionLayer"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer/layout","title":"XRCompositionLayer.layout"}],"pageTitle":"XRCompositionLayer.layout - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}